General.Name: MA Financial Group Ltd
General.Description: MA Financial Group Limited, together with its subsidiaries, provides various financial services. It operates through Asset Management, Lending & Technology, and Corporate Advisory and Equity segments. The Asset Management segment manages funds for institutional, high net worth and retail investors, real estate, hospitality, credit, private equity, and venture capital. The Lending & Technology segment focuses on residential mortgage lending, specialty finance, bespoke receivable funding initiatives, and legal disbursement funding activities. The Corporate Advisory and Equities segment offers strategic and financial advisory services related to mergers and acquisitions; equity capital markets; debt capital markets; and restructuring, research, and cash equities trading, as well as specializes in real estate, credit, technology and small to mid-cap industrial companies. It also provides securities research, sales, and trading execution services to institutional clients.MA Financial Group Limited was founded in 2009 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
